Resource Profile: Oncology Kenya Claim

Official URL: http://example.org/StructureDefinition/oncology-kenya-claim Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-06-30 Computable Name: OncologyKenyaClaim

A FHIR R4-based Claim profile tailored for cancer-related health financing in Kenya. Supports SHA (Social Health Authority) reimbursement workflows and aligns with:

  • Kenya National Cancer Control Strategy 2023–2027,
  • Kenya Cancer Policy 2020–2030,
  • KEMRI cancer reporting and financing infrastructure.

Usages:

  • Examples for this Profile: Claim/example-oncology-claim-nyandarua
